      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Psychic Love 2D\n\nSmall Task #1: Design a mini game for telling fortunes\n\nWhat kind of mechanics could contribute to gameplay loop?\n- time\n- memorization\n- logic\n- intuition\n\nWhat are some concepts that contribute to the overall game theme?\n- tarot cards\n- crystal ball\n- tea leaves\n- palm reading\n\nIdea: Tarot Card Deck Builder",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Psychic Love 2D\n\nSmall Task #1: Design a mini game for telling fortunes\n\nWhat kind of mechanics could contribute to gameplay loop?\n- time\n- memorization\n- logic\n- intuition\n\nWhat are some concepts that contribute to the overall game theme?\n- tarot cards\n- crystal ball\n- tea leaves\n- palm reading\n\nIdea: Tarot Card Deck Builder",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
