      "updated": 1779042695645,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "High ambiguity → risky but flexible readings\nLow tolerance customers → want clarity\nHigh tolerance customers → reward abstract readings",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "High ambiguity → risky but flexible readings\nLow tolerance customers → want clarity\nHigh tolerance customers → reward abstract readings",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "woQLd6Q_Sc1EqG_UlZwS6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -475.0290219704597,
      "y": -1025.8540159061235,
      "width": 639.1795043945312,
      "height": 3600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 383781510,
      "version": 87,
      "versionNonce": 819155723,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776647988805,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Fortunate Misprint\n\nEffect:\n+2 Wealth\n-1 Clarity\n\nFlavor:\nThe prophecy was smudged, but the numbers looked promising.\n\n👉 Good for: greedy plays, messy readings\n\n2. Third Eye Twitch\n\nEffect:\n+2 Clarity\n+1 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nInsight came suddenly, violently, and slightly off-center.\n\n👉 A “risky clarity” card — great for your ambiguity system\n\n3. Lingering Perfume\n\nEffect:\n+2 Romance\n\nModifier Idea:\n+1 Romance if adjacent to another Romance card\n\nFlavor:\nThey swore they moved on. The air disagreed.\n\n👉 Encourages synergy without being complex\n\n4. Empty Coin Purse\n\nEffect:\n+2 Success\n-2 Wealth\n\nFlavor:\nYou will achieve everything. Affording it is another matter.\n\n👉 Nice ironic inversion card\n\n5. Overheard Omen\n\nEffect:\n+1 to all stats\n+2 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nIt wasn’t meant for you, but you heard it anyway.\n\n👉 Great “wildcard” card with a cost\n\n6. Cracked Mirror\n\nEffect:\n+3 Clarity\n-1 Romance\n\nModifier Idea:\nIf first in spread → double Clarity\n\nFlavor:\nThe truth was there. It just refused to look back kindly.\n\n👉 Strong opener card\n\n7. Borrowed Luck\n\nEffect:\n+3 Success\n\nModifier Idea:\nAfter resolution → -1 Success (lingering penalty)\n\nFlavor:\nIt worked. You just don’t know who it was meant for.\n\n👉 Introduces delayed consequences (future design hook)\n\n8. Unsent Letter\n\nEffect:\n+1 Romance\n+1 Clarity\n\nModifier Idea:\n+2 Romance if last in spread\n\nFlavor:\nEverything that needed to be said, perfectly preserved in silence.\n\n👉 Encourages placement strategy\n\n9. Fleeting Windfall\n\nEffect:\n+3 Wealth\n+2 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nIt arrived quickly, loudly, and without explanation.\n\n👉 High risk / high reward\n\n10. Quiet Grave\n\nEffect:\n+2 Clarity\n-1 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nSome answers only come when nothing else does.\n\n👉 Anti-ambiguity card (important for balance)\n\n11. Jealous Star\n\nEffect:\n+2 Romance\n-1 Success\n\nFlavor:\nIt shines brightest when no one else does.\n\n👉 Conflict between stats = good design tension\n\n12. Familiar’s Advice\n\nEffect:\n+1 Clarity\n+1 Success\n\nModifier Idea:\n+1 to all stats if adjacent to 2+ cards\n\nFlavor:\nIt has opinions. You didn’t ask, but it insists.\n\n👉 Great “middle of spread” card",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Fortunate Misprint\n\nEffect:\n+2 Wealth\n-1 Clarity\n\nFlavor:\nThe prophecy was smudged, but the numbers looked promising.\n\n👉 Good for: greedy plays, messy readings\n\n2. Third Eye Twitch\n\nEffect:\n+2 Clarity\n+1 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nInsight came suddenly, violently, and slightly off-center.\n\n👉 A “risky clarity” card — great for your ambiguity system\n\n3. Lingering Perfume\n\nEffect:\n+2 Romance\n\nModifier Idea:\n+1 Romance if adjacent to another Romance card\n\nFlavor:\nThey swore they moved on. The air disagreed.\n\n👉 Encourages synergy without being complex\n\n4. Empty Coin Purse\n\nEffect:\n+2 Success\n-2 Wealth\n\nFlavor:\nYou will achieve everything. Affording it is another matter.\n\n👉 Nice ironic inversion card\n\n5. Overheard Omen\n\nEffect:\n+1 to all stats\n+2 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nIt wasn’t meant for you, but you heard it anyway.\n\n👉 Great “wildcard” card with a cost\n\n6. Cracked Mirror\n\nEffect:\n+3 Clarity\n-1 Romance\n\nModifier Idea:\nIf first in spread → double Clarity\n\nFlavor:\nThe truth was there. It just refused to look back kindly.\n\n👉 Strong opener card\n\n7. Borrowed Luck\n\nEffect:\n+3 Success\n\nModifier Idea:\nAfter resolution → -1 Success (lingering penalty)\n\nFlavor:\nIt worked. You just don’t know who it was meant for.\n\n👉 Introduces delayed consequences (future design hook)\n\n8. Unsent Letter\n\nEffect:\n+1 Romance\n+1 Clarity\n\nModifier Idea:\n+2 Romance if last in spread\n\nFlavor:\nEverything that needed to be said, perfectly preserved in silence.\n\n👉 Encourages placement strategy\n\n9. Fleeting Windfall\n\nEffect:\n+3 Wealth\n+2 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nIt arrived quickly, loudly, and without explanation.\n\n👉 High risk / high reward\n\n10. Quiet Grave\n\nEffect:\n+2 Clarity\n-1 Ambiguity\n\nFlavor:\nSome answers only come when nothing else does.\n\n👉 Anti-ambiguity card (important for balance)\n\n11. Jealous Star\n\nEffect:\n+2 Romance\n-1 Success\n\nFlavor:\nIt shines brightest when no one else does.\n\n👉 Conflict between stats = good design tension\n\n12. Familiar’s Advice\n\nEffect:\n+1 Clarity\n+1 Success\n\nModifier Idea:\n+1 to all stats if adjacent to 2+ cards\n\nFlavor:\nIt has opinions. You didn’t ask, but it insists.\n\n👉 Great “middle of spread” card",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
